7. Resource Model

A Resource is any user-controlled digital asset.

Examples:

Resume
Medical record
Educational credential
Financial statement
AI memory profile

Structure:

{
  "resource_id":"sv:resource:001",
  "owner":"sv:user:001"
}
8. Consent Model

Applications cannot directly access resources.

Instead:

{
  "app_id":"jobportal",
  "resource":"resume",
  "purpose":"candidate screening"
}

The request enters the Consent Engine.

Users can:

Approve
Reject
Revoke
