10. Auditability

Every interaction generates:

{
  "timestamp":"...",
  "actor":"application",
  "action":"read",
  "resource":"resume"
}

Users can inspect access history.

11. Developer Integration

Applications interact through APIs:

POST /consent/request
POST /consent/approve
POST /consent/revoke
GET /resource

This creates a standardized access model.

